{"tid":1791891,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「黃色經濟圈」我今日無比錢去咗睇葉問","createTime":"2019-12-21T08:05:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-21T08:32:11.000Z","uid":281166,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cf25e867f2d49d816fd97dce27adc5b23c8aa5a4","tid":1791891,"uid":281166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T08:05:02.000Z","msg":"是咁的 葉問一至三我都有追開 陪住我成長<br />\n但我真係唔想比錢黃百鳴 所以我同朋友決定睇逃出魔幻紀 <br />\n<br />\n但係行到葉問個戲院門口 突然間又好想睇 最後我地成功係無比錢黃百鳴既情況下睇左葉問<br />\n<br />\n葉問生Cancer，之後想死前幫個仔係美國搵學校，後來同鬼佬又係咁隻秋，最後贏左鬼佬後cancer死<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UKTQWXH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUKTQWXH.jpg&h=4225fbb0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5f4dahN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5f4dahN.png&h=bbebe770&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"98b31b3923aacfe5830a5e72903a0ca2448c2a0a","tid":1791891,"uid":37135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T08:05:48.000Z","msg":"好波"},{"pid":"b7d9178eaa701357d2c60d9b960fb950979f3ce3","tid":1791891,"uid":87780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T08:14:46.000Z","msg":"拍到葉問咁愛國仲要俾個仔去美國讀書?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"197574a1f306e514772afee607227ef6a9c23827","tid":1791891,"uid":44298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T08:16:01.000Z","msg":"咁都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2529c366453dae630ac899bf16491b742bbbe9d","tid":1791891,"uid":74392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T08:17:09.000Z","msg":"hoball"},{"pid":"732ff50fd99739d9ec9083f952066dd683874e4e","tid":1791891,"uid":152584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T08:19:14.000Z","msg":"你點影<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmo